    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the grill to medium-high</p><p>Combine your <strong>white wine vinegar</strong>,<strong> remaining wholegrain mustard </strong>and <strong>chopped chives </strong>in a bowl with a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>salad</strong> to the bowl and toss – this is your <strong>chive salad</strong></p>",
